<section class="work-with-me-hero">
  <h1>I help teams understand their users deeply and make better product decisions through research, strategy and thoughtful design.</h1>
</section>

<section class="services-intro">
  <h2>How We Can Work Together</h2>
  <p>Most of the companies I work with come to me at a point where they know something isn't working but aren't sure where to start, or they have a clear project that needs senior UX thinking and don't have it in-house. I bring research, strategy, design and process support depending on what the situation actually calls for.</p>
  <p>I also use AI strategically throughout my process to handle the repetitive and time-consuming parts of the work, which frees me up to focus on the deeper thinking and means clients get faster, more iterative delivery.</p>
</section>

