      <h3>UX Audit & Strategy</h3>
      <p class="service-subhead">Find what's not working and map a clear path forward</p>
      
      <h4>What's included:</h4>
      <ul>
        <li>UX audit of your current experience</li>
        <li>Competitive analysis (optional)</li>
        <li>User research and testing (if needed)</li>
        <li>Prioritization matrix with recommendations</li>
        <li>Strategic roadmap</li>
      </ul>
      
      <p class="service-meta"><strong>Good fit if:</strong> You know something in your experience needs to change but you're not sure where the real problems are or what to prioritize. You want an outside perspective grounded in research so your team can move forward with confidence.</p>
      
