      <span class="package-label">PACKAGE 2</span>
      <h3>UX Design & Testing</h3>
      <p class="service-subhead">Research, design, and validate a solution before it ships</p>
      
      <h4>What's included:</h4>
      <ul>
        <li>Discovery research to validate or refine the problem</li>
        <li>Information architecture</li>
        <li>Wireframes and prototypes (mobile & desktop)</li>
        <li>Usability testing with real users</li>
        <li>Implementation documentation and handoff</li>
      </ul>
      
      <p class="service-meta"><strong>Good fit if:</strong> You have a specific problem or project that needs to be designed well from the ground up. You're looking for someone who will dig into the research, think through the structure carefully and test the solution before it ships.</p>
      
      <a href="#tally-open=81GvdY&package=Package+2%3A+UX+Design+%26+Testing" class="service-card-cta">Ask about a project</a>
