      <span class="package-label">PACKAGE 3</span>
      <h3>UX Process Building</h3>
      <p class="service-subhead">Build a strong UX practice inside your team</p>
      
      <h4>What's included:</h4>
      <ul>
        <li>UX process design customized to your team's workflow</li>
        <li>Team training (research, testing, strategy)</li>
        <li>Workflow audit, including identifying where AI tools can genuinely improve how your team works</li>
        <li>Ongoing advisory and reviews</li>
        <li>Tool and workflow recommendations</li>
        <li>Hiring guidance when you're ready</li>
      </ul>
      
      <p class="service-meta"><strong>Good fit if:</strong> You're scaling and you know you need more UX rigor, but you're not ready to build out a full team yet. You want someone to help you build the right foundations, train your people and set things up so the work holds together over time.</p>
      
      <a href="#tally-open=81GvdY&package=Package+3%3A+UX+Process+Building" class="service-card-cta">Ask about process work</a>
