    <h3>Ongoing UX Advisory</h3>
    <p class="service-subhead">Strategic UX support without the full-time commitment</p>
    <p>Monthly strategy calls, UX reviews and ongoing guidance for teams who need consistent, senior-level input without a full-time hire. I keep these engagements intentionally scoped so I can give each client real attention, which means I only take on a small number at a time.</p>
